data.description: PRICE REDUCTION OF $5,000!! Motivated seller!! Welcome to a Home of Unmatched Elegance and Comfort! This 4-bed, 2-bath marvel has been transformed into a true masterpiece! Every inch exudes quality and style, promising a lifestyle of luxury. Step into a Kitchen Wonderland! Experience the open-concept kitchen, adorned with soft-close cabinets, top-tier stainless-steel appliances, level 3 granite countertops, and a dazzling subway tile backsplash. The newer vinyl flooring sets the stage, complemented by updated light fixtures and recessed lighting. This Home Boasts Perfection! A NEWER ROOF (2020), a new electric water heater, an updated 200-amp electrical panel, and newer windows ensure a worry-free experience. Turn the key and start living the life you've always dreamed of. Indulge in Your Private Sanctuary! The master bedroom is a haven of tranquility, featuring a spacious en-suite bathroom complete with a floor-to-ceiling porcelain-tiled walk-in shower. Pure bliss! This split-floor plan home welcomes sunshine, creating a cheerful ambiance throughout. Step Outside and Be Amazed! A fully screened patio and a fenced yard invite you to bask in the glorious Florida weather. It's a space where memories are made, and dreams come true. Location, Location, Location! Your new abode is just minutes away from Ridgecrest Park, Taylor Lake, Pelican Golf Course, Indian Rocks Beach, top-rated schools, shopping, and award-winning restaurants. Convenience at its finest! No Worries Here! This home is NOT in a flood zone, and there's NO HOA requirement. The world is your oyster - use it as a short-term rental or investment property. Seize the Moment! Your exclusive viewing awaits. Call today and make this dream home YOUR reality!
